{"tid":1470122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到點折機場公關災難","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:33:19.000Z","uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1bc5bcfc0583d3788957417ca1dc92ffa77566a","tid":1470122,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:15:23.000Z","msg":"旅客冇得返屋企同自己國家一日 <br />\n會嬲會有情緒係好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但香港人唔爭取 我地就以後都冇左自己嘅家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請旅客都包容我地為自己屋企做嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以用以上論點同旅客解釋 爭取同理心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放工機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bead5a36d659c498330347edc27d888d6ea6328f","tid":1470122,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n不分化 不割席"},{"pid":"87192a8b086e5c25dfdd02d90abcce9185ab4122","tid":1470122,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"818都要見"},{"pid":"9e1f36ab7a427369ccd1fe1776fc682e1cd35bf1","tid":1470122,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"要解釋 唔係要道歉"},{"pid":"e737301b60ef5c0ce8b30dc12567640ff3c0d81d","tid":1470122,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:19:09.000Z","msg":"唔好比機場就咁完"},{"pid":"b4ca2eb300536f66a5ade40626baa278d687aa89","tid":1470122,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"開左個好頭 唔好爛尾"},{"pid":"c6ce10770a065d9c63850248b6dd5e7576b2ba1c","tid":1470122,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:20:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84064bfadb55f58bd7fb97fcecdbf60ab06ab096","tid":1470122,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"唔使